<html>
    <head>
        <title>
            Typography
        </title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
       <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>ABBREVIATION</h1>
        <p>It is used to mark up an Abbreviation or Acronym:</p>
        <p><abbr title=Codingal>cdgl</abbr> was founded in 2020.</p>
        <h1>BLOCKQUOTES</h1>
        <p>It is used to present content from another source:</p>
        <blockquote class="blockquote">
            <p>Codingal is on mission to inspire all school kids.</p>
        </blockquote>
        <h1>MULTIPLE CODE LINE</h1>
        <p>For multiple lines code, use pre element;</p>
        <pre>
            Codingal is 
            on mission to 
            inspire all the 
            school kids.
        </pre>
        <h1>KEYBOARDS INPUT </h1>
        <p>To indicate input that is typically entered via the keyboard, use kbd element:</p>
        <p>Use <kbd>Ctrl + p</kbd> to open print dialog box</p>
        <input type="color" name="" id="">
    </body>
</html>
